column_descr: composite primary key/(Winner Id + Loser Id + date)
Name of ATP tennis series (Grand Slam, Masters, International or International Gold)
Maximum number of sets playable in match
ATP Entry ranking of the match winner as of the start of the tournament
ATP Entry ranking of the match loser as of the start of the tournament
Number of games won in 1st set by match winner
Number of games won in 1st set by match loser
Number of games won in 2nd set by match winner
Number of games won in 2nd set by match loser
Number of games won in 3rd set by match winner
Number of games won in 3rd set by match loser
Number of games won in 4th set by match winner
Number of games won in 4th set by match loser
Number of games won in 5th set by match winner
Number of games won in 5th set by match loser
Number of sets won by match winner
Number of sets won by match loser
Comment on the match (Completed, won through retirement of loser, or via Walkover)
Pinnacles Sports odds of match winner
Pinnacles Sports odds of match loser
ATP Entry points of the match winner as of the start of the tournament
ATP Entry points of the match loser as of the start of the tournament
Stan James odds of match winner
Stan James odds of match loser
Maximum odds of match winner (as shown by Oddsportal.com)
Maximum odds of match loser (as shown by Oddsportal.com)
Average odds of match winner (as shown by Oddsportal.com)
Average odds of match loser (as shown by Oddsportal.com)
